'''烏沙科夫獎章'''（{{lang-ru|Медаль Ушакова}}）是[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]及現[[俄羅斯聯邦|俄羅斯聯邦]]的一項軍事[[獎章|獎章]]，以[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]]海军上将[[費奧多爾·費奧多羅維奇·烏沙科夫|費奧多爾·費奧多羅維奇·烏沙科夫]]命名。

== 歷史 ==
烏沙科夫獎章由[[蘇聯最高蘇維埃|蘇聯最高蘇維埃]]在1944年3月設立<ref name="sovietdecree1944">{{cite web | authorlink = Russian Government | title = Decree of the Presidium of the Supreme Soviet of the USSR of  March 3, 1944 | publisher = Wikisource | date = 2011-09-28 | url = http://ru.wikisource.org/wiki/Указ_Президиума_ВС_СССР_от_3.03.1944_об_учреждении_военных_орденов:_ордена_Ушакова_I_и_II_степени_и_ордена_Нахимова_I_и_II_степени | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-12 | archive-date = 2020-12-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201205190249/https://ru.wikisource.org/wiki/%D0%A3%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%B7_%D0%9F%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%B8%D0%B4%D0%B8%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%B0_%D0%92%D0%A1_%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A1%D0%A0_%D0%BE%D1%82_3.03.1944_%D0%BE%D0%B1_%D1%83%D1%87%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B6%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B8_%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8B%D1%85_%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2:_%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B0_%D0%A3%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0_I_%D0%B8_II_%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BF%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8_%D0%B8_%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B0_%D0%9D%D0%B0%D1%85%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0_I_%D0%B8_II_%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BF%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8 | dead-url = no }}</ref>；[[蘇聯解體|蘇聯解體]]後，根據1994年3月2日的[[總統令|總統令]]<ref name="decree442">{{cite web|authorlink=Russian Government |title=Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of March 2, 1994 No 442 |publisher=Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards |date=1999-12-15 |url=http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u442.htm |language=ru |accessdate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205195909/http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u442.htm |archivedate=2012-02-05}}</ref>，此獎章及其設計繼續在俄羅斯聯邦使用，頒發章程曾分別在1999年1月6日和2010年9月7日根據總統令進行修訂<ref name="decree1099">{{cite web | authorlink = Russian Government | title = Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of September 7, 2010 No 1099 | publisher = Russian Gazette | date = 2010-09-07 | url = http://www.rg.ru/2010/09/15/nagrady-dok.html | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | archive-date = 2016-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310205827/http://rg.ru/2010/09/15/nagrady-dok.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="decree19">{{cite web|authorlink=Russian Government |title=Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of January 6, 1999 No 19 |publisher=Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards |date=1999-12-15 |url=http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u19.htm |language=ru |accessdate=2012-02-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205195833/http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u19.htm |archivedate=2012-02-05}}</ref> 。

== 頒發 ==
烏沙科夫獎章是頒發予在戰時和平時在蘇聯海域保護的海上邊界、危險的軍事任務中顯示勇氣和勇敢的[[蘇聯海軍|蘇聯海軍]][[水手|水手]]、[[士兵|士兵]]、[[士官|士官]]和[[軍官|軍官]]。由1944年到1991年蘇聯解體，烏沙科夫獎章一共被頒發過估計14,000至16,000次<ref name="ruwiki article">{{cite web | title = Медаль Ушакова – Medal of Ushakov | publisher = Russian Wikipedia | url = http://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C_%D0%A3%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0 | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | archive-date = 2015-05-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150505020458/https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C_%D0%A3%D1%88%D0%B0%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 獎章外貌 ==
烏沙科夫獎章是一塊直徑為36mm的圓形銀牌，邊緣凸起；獎章正面中心有烏沙科夫的浮雕半身像，上方有一行字“海軍上將★烏沙科夫”（俄語：АДМИРАЛ★УШАКОВ），獎章背面則有一個錨<ref name="statute">{{cite web | authorlink = Russian Government | title = Statute of the Medal of Ushakov | publisher = Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards | date = 2010-09-07 | url = http://award.gov.ru/ushakov_medal.html | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | archive-date = 2011-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111207065234/http://award.gov.ru/ushakov_medal.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。烏沙科夫獎章的綬帶為一[[五邊形|五邊形]]，中間有一條銀色的金屬鏈<ref name="statute"/>。

